A man visits the 2021 International Contemporary Art Fair (FIAC) during a preview at the Grand Palais Ephemere in Paris, France, on Oct. 20, 2021. The fair which runs from Oct. 21 to 24, brings together modern and contemporary art works and featurs a wide variety of media such as painting, sculpture, photography, installations, videos, performances, digital arts, etc. (Xinhua/Gao Jing)  